  "detailed_description": "Challenging emergent arcade shooting fun! Plan, time and bounce your shots, how large a combo you can score with a single shot.<br><br>Can you 100% and 3 star each level?   It’s not as easy as you think! <br><br>With every pixel in each level a dynamic physics object, the emergent possibilities for each level are endless.<br><br>Features:<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Synth-wave glitch styling<br></li><li>42 challenging puzzle, wave and boss levels<br></li><li>100% pixel physics<br></li><li>100% real gameplay<br></li><li>Space unicorn that poops mines<br></li><li>Local high scores<br></li><li>Designed to be played on restored arcade cabinets</li></ul>",
